<p>Next, I had to find my wifeâ€™s User Folder - they were found in a folder called â€˜Previous Systems,â€™ in a directory with the date and time of my first install attempt.Â  <a href="http://www.gbradhopkins.com/archives/upload/2007/10/directories.jpg" title="View Window">View the window and path.</a></p>

